{"id":9610,"date":"2019-05-16T08:46:39","date_gmt":"2019-05-16T08:46:39","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/wappier.com\/?p=9610"},"modified":"2022-08-12T10:03:50","modified_gmt":"2022-08-12T10:03:50","slug":"casual-connect-london-2019","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wappier.com\/casual-connect-london-2019\/","title":{"rendered":"Casual Connect London 2019"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"9610\" class=\"elementor elementor-9610\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-section-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-47606e9 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"47606e9\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-3817dea8\" data-id=\"3817dea8\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-51698d80 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"51698d80\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><!-- wp:heading --><\/p>\n<h2>wappier does #CCLondon!<\/h2>\n<p><!-- \/wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><strong>28-30 May 2019:<\/strong> Casual Connect London, YEAH!&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Exploring how creativity and business can merge to create beautiful games. Over 100 leaders in established and emerging markets of the mobile gaming industry will be there to cover game design, esports, live\/ops, publishing, and next-generation technology. We wouldn&#8217;t miss it for the world!<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>What we are looking forward to the most? Our panel session on stage entitled <strong>&#8220;Mobile Gaming Today&#8221;<\/strong>. Our VP of Business Development, Ted Verani, will be moderating the panel with four mobile game experts:<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Enric Cabestany, General Manager Europe @ <strong>IGG<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Vera Rabkina, Product Manager @ <strong>Gismart<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Kyu Lee, President @ <strong>Gamevil<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Fraser MacInnes, Director of Business Development @ <strong>Scopely<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>12 different content tracks:<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:list --><!-- wp:image {\"id\":9612} --><\/p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure id=\"attachment_9856\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-9856\" style=\"width: 1376px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img class=\"wp-image-9856 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/wappier.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/casual-connect-content-tracks.png\" alt=\"wappier at Casual Connect Europe 2019 - Content Tracks\" width=\"1376\" height=\"196\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wappier.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/casual-connect-content-tracks.png 1376w, https:\/\/wappier.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/casual-connect-content-tracks-300x43.png 300w, https:\/\/wappier.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/casual-connect-content-tracks-768x109.png 768w, https:\/\/wappier.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/casual-connect-content-tracks-1024x146.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1376px) 100vw, 1376px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-9856\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">wappier at Casual Connect Europe 2019 &#8211; Content Tracks<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<p><!-- \/wp:image --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>Summary: &#8220;The mobile market represents around half of all global games revenues, and opportunities abound for savvy developers, but how can today&#8217;s game makers stand out from the crowd on the App Store and Google Play? <strong>How can they not only acquire users but retain them?<\/strong> What are the keys to success and what lies ahead for the booming mobile space? This panel of experts will discuss the vital points developers need to understand.&#8221;<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>Track: Industry Insights &#8211; Learn more <a href=\"http:\/\/europe.casualconnect.org\/content.html?speaker=mobilepanel\">about the panel and its awesome speakers<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>Wanna know more about what <strong>Intelligent Revenue Management<\/strong> is? Automated Loyalty, <a href=\"https:\/\/wappier.com\/global-pricing\/\">Pricing Optimization<\/a> and Advanced Audience Management can help you supercharge your mobile game&#8217;s monetization.&nbsp;<\/p><p>Reach out to us at events@wappier.com or contact <a href=\"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/in\/tedverani\/\">Ted<\/a> directly to arrange a what we can guarantee will be a fun intro chat with wappier.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>See you there!<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>wappier does #CCLondon! 28-30 May 2019: Casual Connect London, YEAH!&nbsp; Exploring how creativity and business can merge to create beautiful games. Over 100 leaders in established and emerging markets of the mobile gaming industry will be there to cover game design, esports, live\/ops, publishing, and next-generation technology. We wouldn&#8217;t miss it for the world! What [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","